      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for those seeking functional transportation at an affordable price point. The exterior shows typical signs of age, including several noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and some fading in the paint finish. Inside, the cabin is intact but displays wear on the upholstery and carpets consistent with regular use. Mechanically, the car starts and drives, though it may benefit from a tune-up and some minor suspension work in the near future to improve ride quality. It is a solid choice for a daily driver if you don't mind some cosmetic imperfections.",
