      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and a factory 6-speed manual transmission. To ensure long-term structural integrity, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced, and the dual-VANOS timing system has been overhauled for optimal cam phasing. The chassis is enhanced with Bilstein dampers and refreshed bushings, maintaining the precise handling characteristics these M-cars are known for. While the Alpine White paint shows minor road wear, the mechanical vitals\u2014including the variable M differential lock and throttle response\u2014are in peak form. A turn-key enthusiast build with all major preventative maintenance addressed.",
