      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and reliability. The exterior features a deep metallic finish that retains a brilliant shine, showing only the minor, expected road peppering on the front fascia and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel. Inside, the cabin is a testament to careful ownership; the premium leather upholstery has been regularly conditioned and remains supple, with only light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every electronic component, from the premium surround-sound system to the heated seats and navigation, operates flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is in its prime. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, with a complete folder of receipts included. The engine runs quietly and delivers smooth, responsive power, while the transmission shifts are seamless. Recent maintenance includes a fresh synthetic oil change and a new set of high-performance all-season tires with plenty of tread remaining. This is an honest, well-cared-for example ready for its next owner to drive with total confidence.",
